    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The disclaimer is intended to only display when the data directory does not yet exist, as this will coincide with most instances of \"first run\".\n\nFor example, `geth account new` will create an account and store it in the datadir. Subsequent runs of geth, i.e. `geth account list` or `geth attach` shoudl not show the disclaimer again.\n",
